23
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:47,910
Good morning.

24
00:01:48,070 --> 00:01:48,670
Commander Xiao.

25
00:01:48,990 --> 00:01:49,590
Miss He.

26
00:01:49,910 --> 00:01:51,150
Let's have breakfast together.

27
00:01:53,030 --> 00:01:53,660
